data.description: Introducing a stunning single-family home nestled in the sought-after community Crane Landing in North Fort Myers. This exquisite residence offers a charming and contemporary design, boasting both style and functionality. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a spacious living area featuring an abundance of natural light and modern finishes. The open concept floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating the perfect space for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. The kitchen is a chef's delight. This home features four generous bedrooms and two bathrooms. Step outside to the serene backyard and enjoy the Florida weather. The location is superb close to shopping centers, restaurants, parks and major highways. Fort Myers beaches are just a short drive away. Don't miss this incredible opportunity, schedule a showing today and discover the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience that this property offers.
